---
title: Honey Halloumi & Creamy Avo Salad with Jammy Eggs & Toasted Almonds
description: Don’t worry, this is nothing like your garden variety salad - this one has flavour popping like fireworks. Salty and squeaky
halloumi next to a soft boiled egg, all wrapped up in crunchy cos lettuce sure sounds like an exciting take on a salad - but we’ll let you try it for yourself.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6792f760d0643436c326530c-c22839ed.jpeg
